snippet.title: Indigo Gaming
snippet.description:
Insightful game analysis, reviews and retrospectives with an emphasis on historical importance and their impact on the industry. No politics.

I host livestreams every Wednesday at 8PM Eastern on my 2nd channel.

PC Specifications:

AMD Ryzen 9 3950X 3.5GHz [4.7GHz Turbo] 16 Cores/32 Threads
ASUS ROG STRIX X570-E Gaming ATX
NZXT Kraken X52 240mm RGB CPU Liquid Cooling System w/ Copper Cold Plate
32GB Kingston HyperX Predator DDR4/3000MHz Dual Channel Memory
ASUS ROG Strix 2080 Ti
1TB Samsung 860 EVO Series M.2 SATA-III 6 Gb/s SSD
2x 6TB SATA-III 6.0Gb/s 64MB Cache 7200RPM HDD
Windows 10 Pro (64-bit Edition)
Asus ROG Swift PG27UQ 27" Gaming Monitor 4K UHD 144Hz G-SYNC HDR
